To create the same shape in Python using the turtle library, you can use the following code:

```python
import turtle

t = turtle.Turtle()
t.set_screen_size(100, 100)
t.set_color('black')
t.begin_fill()
t.polygon(points, fillcolor='black')
t.end_fill()
t.show()
```

This code sets up a turtle with a black color, creates a polygon using the given points, and then displays the shape.</s>